text: Škrlovica () is a small village east of Dvorska Vas in the Municipality of Velike Lašče in central Slovenia. The municipality is part of the traditional region of Lower Carniola and is now included in the Central Slovenia Statistical Region.Velike Lašče municipal site ==References== ==External links== *Škrlovica on Geopedia Category:Populated places in the Municipality of Velike Lašče
